[{"type":"paragraph text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":1,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"So these three men ceased to answer Job, because he was righteous in his own eyes.  "},{"type":"paragraph text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":2,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"Then the wrath of Elihu the son of Barachel, the Buzite, of the family of Ram, was kindled against Job. His wrath was kindled because he justified himself rather than God.  "},{"type":"paragraph text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":3,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"Also his wrath was kindled against his three friends, because they had found no answer, and yet had condemned Job.  "},{"type":"paragraph text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":4,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"Now Elihu had waited to speak to Job, because they were elder than he.  "},{"type":"paragraph text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":5,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"When Elihu saw that there was no answer in the mouth of these three men, his wrath was kindled. "},{"type":"paragraph end"},{"type":"break"},{"type":"paragraph start"},{"type":"paragraph text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":6,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"Elihu the son of Barachel the Buzite answered, "},{"type":"paragraph end"},{"type":"stanza start"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":6,"sectionNumber":2,"value":"“I am young, and you are very old; "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":6,"sectionNumber":3,"value":"Therefore I held back, and didn’t dare show you my opinion. "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":7,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"I said, ‘Days should speak, "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":7,"sectionNumber":2,"value":"and multitude of years should teach wisdom.’ "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":8,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"But there is a spirit in man, "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":8,"sectionNumber":2,"value":"and the Spirit of the Almighty gives them understanding. "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":9,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"It is not the great who are wise, "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":9,"sectionNumber":2,"value":"nor the aged who understand justice. "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":10,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"Therefore I said, ‘Listen to me; "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":10,"sectionNumber":2,"value":"I also will show my opinion.’ "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"stanza end"},{"type":"stanza start"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":10,"sectionNumber":3,"value":" "},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":11,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"“Behold, I waited for your words, "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":11,"sectionNumber":2,"value":"and I listened for your reasoning, "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":11,"sectionNumber":3,"value":"while you searched out what to say. "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":12,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"Yes, I gave you my full attention, "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":12,"sectionNumber":2,"value":"but there was no one who convinced Job, "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":12,"sectionNumber":3,"value":"or who answered his words, among you. "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":13,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"Beware lest you say, ‘We have found wisdom. "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":13,"sectionNumber":2,"value":"God may refute him, not man;’ "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":14,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"for he has not directed his words against me; "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":14,"sectionNumber":2,"value":"neither will I answer him with your speeches. "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"stanza end"},{"type":"stanza start"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":14,"sectionNumber":3,"value":" "},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":15,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"“They are amazed. They answer no more. "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":15,"sectionNumber":2,"value":"They don’t have a word to say. "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":16,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"Shall I wait, because they don’t speak, "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":16,"sectionNumber":2,"value":"because they stand still, and answer no more? "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":17,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"I also will answer my part, "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":17,"sectionNumber":2,"value":"and I also will show my opinion. "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":18,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"For I am full of words. "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":18,"sectionNumber":2,"value":"The spirit within me constrains me. "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":19,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"Behold, my breast is as wine which has no vent; "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":19,"sectionNumber":2,"value":"like new wineskins it is ready to burst. "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":20,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"I will speak, that I may be refreshed. "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":20,"sectionNumber":2,"value":"I will open my lips and answer. "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":21,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"Please don’t let me respect any man’s person, "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":21,"sectionNumber":2,"value":"neither will I give flattering titles to any man. "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":22,"sectionNumber":1,"value":"For I don’t know how to give flattering titles, "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"line text","chapterNumber":32,"verseNumber":22,"sectionNumber":2,"value":"or else my Maker would soon take me away. "},{"type":"line break"},{"type":"stanza end"},{"type":"stanza start"},{"type":"stanza end"},{"type":"stanza start"}]